INSERT INTO `pp_posts` VALUES (6,1,'2010-11-05 07:49:08','2010-11-05 07:49:08','Do you sometimes feel like you are the only Christian in your place of work? Would you like to meet to pray with other people about your work or colleagues? I work in the Clifton Moor area and we meet with other Christians to pray, every week, Tuesday 1pm-2pm at the Bowling Alley.','Home','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-2','','','2010-11-05 07:49:08','2010-11-05 07:49:08','',2,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/2010/11/05/2-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(2,1,'2010-11-05 07:25:22','2010-11-05 07:25:22','Do you sometimes feel like you are the only Christian in your place of work? Would you like to meet to pray with other people about your work or colleagues? I work in the Clifton Moor area and we meet with other Christians to pray, every week, Tuesday 1pm-2pm at the Bowling Alley.\r\n\r\nFor more details please keep reading this site or contact me on 07906 028412 or <a href=\"mailto:simon@prayer4work.com\">simon@prayer4work.com</a>\r\n\r\nWe are also on <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/pages/Prayer4Work/117837714946057\">facebook</a> and twitter <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/prayer4work\">@prayer4work</a>','Prayer4Work','','publish','closed','closed','','about','','','2010-11-19 16:59:20','2010-11-19 16:59:20','',0,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(4,1,'2010-11-05 07:25:22','2010-11-05 07:25:22','This is an example of a WordPress page, you could edit this to put information about yourself or your site so readers know where you are coming from. You can create as many pages like this one or sub-pages as you like and manage all of your content inside of WordPress.','About','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision','','','2010-11-05 07:25:22','2010-11-05 07:25:22','',2,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/?p=4',0,'revision','',0),(8,1,'2010-11-05 15:34:56','2010-11-05 15:34:56','Do you sometimes feel like you are the only Christian in your place of work? Would you like to meet to pray with other people about your work or colleagues? I work in the Clifton Moor area and we meet with other Christians to pray, every week, Tuesday 1pm-2pm at the Bowling Alley.','Home','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-3','','','2010-11-05 15:34:56','2010-11-05 15:34:56','',2,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/2010/11/05/2-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(9,1,'2010-11-08 12:47:59','2010-11-08 12:47:59','<h2>Location</h2>\r\nEvery Tuesday lunchtime (1pm - 2pm) we meet at the Clifton Moor bowling alley. Please pray for the staff of the <a href=\"http://www.tenpin.co.uk/\">bowling alley</a> that they may see what we are trying to do (and order a drink or some food to support their business).\r\n<br/>\r\n<iframe width=\"425\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.co.uk/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=prayer4work&amp;sll=53.990414,-1.100843&amp;sspn=0.004289,0.021973&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=prayer4work&amp;hnear=&amp;ll=53.989758,-1.101894&amp;spn=0.017662,0.036478&amp;z=14&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><br/>\r\n<strong>Stirling Road, \r\nClifton Moor, \r\nYork, \r\nNorth Yorkshire \r\nYO30 4WZ</strong>','Location','','publish','open','open','','location','','','2010-11-08 20:57:35','2010-11-08 20:57:35','',0,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/',1,'page','',0),(10,1,'2010-11-08 12:47:51','2010-11-08 12:47:51','','Auto Draft','','inherit','open','open','','9-revision','','','2010-11-08 12:47:51','2010-11-08 12:47:51','',9,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/2010/11/08/9-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(11,1,'2010-11-08 12:48:23','2010-11-08 12:48:23','The following companies all have people who regularly come to our prayer meetings. If you want to come along I will happily put your website here. One of the side benefits of meeting together is that we get to know each other better and there may be opportunities to help each others businesses.\r\n\r\nI work for <a href=\"http://www.eurosafeuk.co.uk\">Eurosafe UK</a> They are a health and safety consultancy company specialising in Asbestos surveys, Construction Projects and IT services for the Construction Industry. This led them to release a range of cloud computing products called <a href=\"http://www.cloudsuk.com\">Clouds UK</a> \r\n\r\nAlan Brown runs a successful Financial Services Company <a href=\"http://www.sjpp.co.uk/alanbrown/index.html\">Brown\'s Wealth Management</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.tenpin.co.uk/\">Tenpin Bowling</a> is the bowling alley in Clifton Moor where we meet each week. Please pray for the staff there and that we can continue meeting here.\r\n\r\nThis group is not tied to one church or any denomination, all who want to meet and pray are welcome. We do have links with the following churches because members of the group worship there.\r\n<a href=\"http://www.stmichaelsyork.org/\">St Michael le Belfrey</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.cliftonparish.org.uk/\">Clifton Parish Church</a>','Useful Links','','publish','open','open','','useful-links','','','2010-11-08 21:48:07','2010-11-08 21:48:07','',0,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/',2,'page','',0),(12,1,'2010-11-08 12:48:06','2010-11-08 12:48:06','','Auto Draft','','inherit','open','open','','11-revision','','','2010-11-08 12:48:06','2010-11-08 12:48:06','',11,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/2010/11/08/11-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(13,1,'2010-11-08 12:47:59','2010-11-08 12:47:59','','Location','','inherit','open','open','','9-revision-2','','','2010-11-08 12:47:59','2010-11-08 12:47:59','',9,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/2010/11/08/9-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(14,1,'2010-11-08 12:49:13','2010-11-08 12:49:13','','Location','','inherit','open','open','','9-revision-3','','','2010-11-08 12:49:13','2010-11-08 12:49:13','',9,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/2010/11/08/9-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(15,1,'2010-11-08 12:49:26','2010-11-08 12:49:26','','Location','','inherit','open','open','','9-revision-4','','','2010-11-08 12:49:26','2010-11-08 12:49:26','',9,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/2010/11/08/9-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(16,1,'2010-11-08 12:48:23','2010-11-08 12:48:23','','Useful Links','','inherit','open','open','','11-revision-2','','','2010-11-08 12:48:23','2010-11-08 12:48:23','',11,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/2010/11/08/11-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(17,1,'2010-09-14 12:53:27','2010-09-14 12:53:27','I never thought I would say this but I like praying out loud.\r\n\r\nOn a Tuesday I have plenty of opportunities to pray. I start the day by getting myself to St Mikes Dynamic Prayer meeting which starts at 7am. It is a struggle for me getting out of bed but I always appreciate it when I am there. We typically worship and praise God, often about church stuff, but also sometimes other things. Today we prayed for Alpha, and for YoYo. And it ends with a croissant and time to chat with people.\r\n\r\nAt lunch time it is time for my prayer group for Clifton Moor, unfortunately there was only two of us this week. But it was a great opportunity to pray for the area, and give thanks for my busy day. I was expecting to not be able to get away or to have trouble when I returned, thankfully that didnâ€™t happen. Could this be down to prayer.\r\n\r\nRecently I have been going to Conversations, which is a church for young people, based in a pub in town. I went to one of their cells tonight. It was good and everyone was friendly,  but when it came to the prayer time, I was surprised that everyone prayed in their heads, not out loud. I am so used to my cell praying out loud and for each other, I found it difficult to do. I know everyone spends time with God in different ways, but I am reminded of what people said to me when I started praying that we encourage each other with our prayers, If I pray out loud it encourages someone else to pray.','My Tuesday prayer day','','publish','open','open','','tuesday-prayer-day','','','2010-11-20 17:12:35','2010-11-20 17:12:35','',0,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/?p=17',0,'post','',0),(18,1,'2010-11-08 12:53:20','2010-11-08 12:53:20','','Blog Post','','inherit','open','open','','17-revision','','','2010-11-08 12:53:20','2010-11-08 12:53:20','',17,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/2010/11/08/17-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(19,1,'2010-11-08 12:57:29','2010-11-08 12:57:29','','Blog','','publish','open','open','','blog','','','2010-11-13 08:31:43','2010-11-13 08:31:43','',0,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/?p=19',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(20,1,'2010-11-08 12:57:57','2010-11-08 12:57:57',' ','','','publish','open','open','','20','','','2010-11-13 08:31:43','2010-11-13 08:31:43','',0,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/?p=20',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(21,1,'2010-11-08 12:57:57','2010-11-08 12:57:57',' ','','','publish','open','open','','21','','','2010-11-13 08:31:43','2010-11-13 08:31:43','',0,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/?p=21',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(22,1,'2010-11-08 12:57:57','2010-11-08 12:57:57','Do you sometimes feel like you are the only Christian in your place of work? Would you like to meet to pray with other people about your work or colleagues? I work in the Clifton Moor area and we meet with other Christians to pray, every week, Tuesday 1pm-2pm at the Bowling Alley.','','','publish','open','open','','22','','','2010-11-13 08:31:42','2010-11-13 08:31:42','',0,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/?p=22',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(23,1,'2010-11-08 12:53:27','2010-11-08 12:53:27','Post','Blog Post','','inherit','open','open','','17-revision-2','','','2010-11-08 12:53:27','2010-11-08 12:53:27','',17,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/2010/11/08/17-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(24,1,'2010-11-08 16:50:54','2010-11-08 16:50:54','<h2>GENESIS: The coming into being of something; the origin</h2>\r\nThe genesis of this idea goes back to April 2010. At that time I went to a Church weekend run by St Michael le Belfrey, the theme of the weekend was transformation, I heard some very interesting talks and seminars and found myself thinking what can I do to start a mini transformation.\r\n\r\nAt the same time I was getting very frustrated at how un-christian I felt during my working day, and wishing that I could be a better christian.\r\n\r\nLater in the year I went to a christian summer conference called <a href=\"http://www.new-wine.org/\">New Wine</a>, again I heard a lot about transformation and what small churches were doing to improve their communities. It was during this week, while immersed in the christian life that the idea came to me. \r\n\r\nI work in a business park that has lots and lots of different companies, while I don\'t know any Christians that work for my company, surely there must be some in the company next door. If I could meet with other Christians once a week, we could help support each other in prayer and build each other up.\r\n\r\nAfter I had the idea it was time to decide what to do to implement it. I spoke to various people from church which gave me some possible contacts. I then met with a couple of them at one of their homes, until we decided that a public venue would be better and less intimidating.\r\n\r\nWe have now been meeting for over two months, praying for each other and the local businesses.','Genesis','','publish','open','open','','genesis','','','2010-11-08 21:17:30','2010-11-08 21:17:30','',0,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/',4,'page','',0),(25,1,'2010-11-08 16:50:48','2010-11-08 16:50:48','','Genesis','','inherit','open','open','','24-revision','','','2010-11-08 16:50:48','2010-11-08 16:50:48','',24,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/2010/11/08/24-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(26,1,'2010-11-08 16:51:36','2010-11-08 16:51:36',' ','','','publish','open','open','','26','','','2010-11-13 08:31:43','2010-11-13 08:31:43','',0,'http://prayer.funky-si.co.uk/?p=26',6,'nav_menu_item','',0),(27,1,'2010-11-08 16:50:54','2010-11-08 16:50:54','','Genesis','','inherit','open','open','','24-revision-2','','','2010-11-08 16:50:54','2010-11-08 16:50:54','',24,'http: