er the last 5 years.  What began as <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/akismet/\">a single WordPress plugin</a> is now available in <a href=\"http://akismet.com/development/\">24 plugins and 14 libraries</a>.</p>\n<p>What do you think of Akismet&#8217;s redesign? Do you use Akismet on your blog? If not, how do you protect your blog from spam?</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~4/RuEEN0KFOCk\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 05 Nov 2010 13:00:29 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"James Huff\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:19;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:2:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"Matt: Implications Of Blogging\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"http://ma.tt/?p=36033\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"http://ma.tt/2010/11/implications-of-blogging/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:384:\"<p>Philip Leigh writes about <a href=\"http://www.mediapost.com/publications/?fa=Articles.showArticle&amp;art_aid=137079\">The Implications Of Blogging for MediaPost</a>. &#8220;[M]uch like the printing press transformed publishing, the true cultural significance of blogging &#8212; which is only incipient at present &#8212; will be a consequence of its production process.&#8221;</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 04 Nov 2010 15:28:30 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Matt\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:20;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:2:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"Akismet: Our new designer\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"http://blog.akismet.com/?p=434\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://blog.akismet.com/2010/11/04/our-new-designer/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3822:\"<p>Hey there.Â  My name is Dave Martin.Â  I just joined the <a href=\"http://www.akismet.com/\">Akismet</a> team at <a href=\"http://www.automattic.com\">Automattic</a>.Â  I thought it  might be fun to introduce myself and talk about how I landed a job at  Automattic.</p>\n<p>I just moved back to the U.S. from Sydney, Australia.Â  I was there for 2  years while working as the <abbr title=\"User Interface\">UI</abbr> designer for Campaign Monitor.Â  I learned a  lot while at Campaign Monitor.Â  A couple of the biggest takeaways were:</p>\n<ol>\n<li> Data driven design can be super valuable.</li>\n<li>Obsessing over every detail will pay off in the end.</li>\n<li>The importance of providing great support.</li>\n<li>How rewarding it is to work for a company that cares about their  products (more than just making money).</li>\n</ol>\n<p>When I started looking at companies in the U.S.,Â  I was worried that  I&#8217;d never find another company like Campaign Monitor.Â  Basically, I  wanted to work for a cool company that was passionate about their work.Â   I wanted to work with smart people.Â  I also wanted to work from home if  at all possible (I&#8217;m a sucker for 3:00PM naps).</p>\n<p>After looking at a bunch of companies, I stumbled across a  &#8220;designer&#8221; job listing at Automattic.Â  I knew that there would probably  be hundreds of applicants, so I decided to keep my application short.Â  I  wrote 3 lines introducing myself, gave 8 examples of my work, and sent  it off.</p>\n<p>Within a couple of days I had two interviews over Skype (which was  great, because I was still in Sydney).Â  I was then given a test project  to redesign the Akismet marketing site.Â  Since I was still working  full-time, I was only able to work on the redesign for an hour or two  each night.Â  The hiring process and test project lasted about a month and a  half before they made me an offer.</p>\n<p>Now that I&#8217;m working with Akismet full-time, my focus will be to  improve the user experience of the Akismet plugin and WordPress comments  in general.Â  I&#8217;ll also be working hard to simplify the sign up process  on the Akismet marketing site.</p>\n<p>Please let me know if you have any suggestions/feedback about Akismet.Â  I&#8217;d love to hear your thoughts.</p>\n<br />  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/akismet.wordpress.com/434/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/akismet.wordpress.com/434/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godelicious/akismet.wordpress.com/434/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/delicious/akismet.wordpress.com/434/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gofacebook/akismet.wordpress.com/434/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/facebook/akismet.wordpress.com/434/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gotwitter/akismet.wordpress.com/434/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/twitter/akismet.wordpress.com/434/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gostumble/akismet.wordpress.com/434/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/stumble/akismet.wordpress.com/434/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godigg/akismet.wordpress.com/434/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/digg/akismet.wordpress.com/434/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/goreddit/akismet.wordpress.com/434/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/reddit/akismet.wordpress.com/434/\" /></a> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=blog.akismet.com&amp;blog=116920&amp;post=434&amp;subd=akismet&amp;ref=&amp;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 04 Nov 2010 13:43:13 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Dave Martin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:21;a:6:{s:4:\"